Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.82,0:23:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此話當真嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.52,0:23:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.03,0:23:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸村
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.85,0:23:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主公
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.98,0:23:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸村
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.18,0:23:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集終於輪到我們出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.81,0:23:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠勝 攻擊形態 殲滅敵軍
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.11,0:24:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰國BASARA的周邊不斷登陸於Animate
